rows.name: Have you got what I need?

rows.label: qst640302_msg0201
rows.name:
The Ripbik Ellook is a rare breed that
lives in the lower regions of Luxuria.

rows.label: qst640302_msg0202
rows.name:
That's why few know how to work
the materials harvested from it.
In this town, none but me.

rows.label: qst640302_msg0203
rows.name:
And that's why my works command
such high prices.

rows.label: qst640302_msg0204
rows.name:
And THAT is why I live in such a
lofty place.
